//Summary: Returns the absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
//Description: Dojo does not handle the case where the parameters in the URL are delimeted by the "/" forward slash. Therefore, in order to
// workaround the issue, all AJAX requests must be done using absolute URLs rather than relative.
//Returns: The absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
function getAbsoluteURL() {
if (absoluteURL != "") {
var currentURL = document.URL;
var currentProtocol = "";
if (currentURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
currentProtocol = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL.indexOf("://"));
}
var savedProtocol = "";
if (absoluteURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
savedProtocol = absoluteURL.substring(0, absoluteURL.indexOf("://"));
}
if (currentProtocol != savedProtocol) {
absoluteURL = currentProtocol + absoluteURL.substring(absoluteURL.indexOf("://"));
}
}
return absoluteURL;
}
//Summary: Returns the path pointing to the shared image directory.

//Returns: The path to reference color-dependant image files.
function getStyleDirectoryPath() {
return styleDirectoryPath;
}

<script type="text/javascript">
var PLEASE_WAIT = 'Please wait...';
var WTS_DISTANCE = 'Distance from';
var ERROR_ZIP_CODE_DELIVERY = 'An error(s) has occured. Please try again.';
var TIMEOUT_ZIP_CODE_DELIVERY = 'Your request has timed out. Please try again.';
var EMPTY_SENDER_NAME = 'Sender name/email address is not valid. Please try again.';
var EMPTY_RECIPIENT_NAME = 'Not all required fields were entered. Please try again.';
var EMPTY_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS = 'Recipient email address is not valid. Please try again.';
var ERROR_EMAIL_DELIVERY = 'An error(s) has occured. Please try again.';
var TIMEOUT_EMAIL_DELIVERY = 'Your request has timed out. Please try again.';
var VERIFY_NOT_ROBOT = 'Please verify that you are not a robot.';
var SERVICE_RETURNED_EXCEPTION_MESSAGE = 'There was a problem validating your form, please resubmit your form or call 1-888-HAVERTY for assistance.';
wc.service.declare({
id: "EMailSendCmd",
actionId: "EMailSendCmd",
url: getAbsoluteURL() + "EMailSendCmd",
formId: ""
,successHandler: function(serviceResponse) {
if (serviceResponse.result == "error"){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = SERVICE_RETURNED_EXCEPTION_MESSAGE;
dojo.byId("eMailSendButton").disabled=false;
grecaptcha.reset();
}else if(serviceResponse.result == "success") {
$("#SendMsgForm").hide();
$("#eMailSendHeader").hide();
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = "Your email has been sent. Thank you.";
cmCreatePageElementTag(document.title, "Email A Friend Sent");
$('#SendMsgForm')[0].reset();
grecaptcha.reset();
} else if(serviceResponse.error == "CAPTCHA_ERROR") {
grecaptcha.reset();
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = VERIFY_NOT_ROBOT;
dojo.byId("eMailSendButton").disabled=false;
}
else {
grecaptcha.reset();
throw(Exception);
}
}
,failureHandler: function(serviceResponse) {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = ERROR_EMAIL_DELIVERY ;
dojo.byId("eMailSendButton").disabled=false;
grecaptcha.reset();
}
});
function sendEmailFriend() {
var recipient = dojo.byId("recipient").value;
var sender_name = dojo.byId("sender_name").value;
var sender_email = dojo.byId("sender_email").value;
var optional_message = dojo.byId("optional_message").value;
var at="@";
var dot=".";
var sku = productDisplayJS.getFormattedSelectedSku();
$("#sku").val(sku);
if (sender_name == "") {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_NAME;
return;
}
var lat=recipient.indexOf(at);
var lstr=recipient.length;
var ldot=recipient.indexOf(dot);
if (recipient.indexOf(at)==-1 || recipient.indexOf(at)==0 || recipient.indexOf(at)==lstr){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS;
return;
}
if (recipient.indexOf(dot)==-1 || recipient.indexOf(dot)==0 || recipient.indexOf(dot)==lstr){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS;
return;
}
if (recipient == "") {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_NAME;
return;
}
if (recipient.length < 5) {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_ADDRESS;
return;
}
var lat=sender_email.indexOf(at);
var lstr=sender_email.length;
var ldot=sender_email.indexOf(dot);
if (sender_email.indexOf(at)==-1 || sender_email.indexOf(at)==0 || sender_email.indexOf(at)==lstr){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_SENDER_NAME;
return;
}
if (sender_email.indexOf(dot)==-1 || sender_email.indexOf(dot)==0 || sender_email.indexOf(dot)==lstr){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_SENDER_NAME;
return;
}
if (sender_email == "") {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_RECIPIENT_NAME;
return;
}
if (sender_email.length < 5) {
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = EMPTY_SENDER_NAME;
return;
}
//Verify that user is not a robot using reCAPTCHA
if (grecaptcha && grecaptcha.getResponse().length == 0){
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = VERIFY_NOT_ROBOT;
return;
}
dojo.byId("eMailSendButton").disabled=true;
dojo.byId("eMailSendResult").innerHTML = PLEASE_WAIT;
var productName = $('#product-display-name').html();
cmCreateElementTag(productName, "Email a Friend Sent");
wc.service.getServiceById("EMailSendCmd").formId = "SendMsgForm";
wc.service.invoke("EMailSendCmd");
}
</script>

/**
* Clears the progress bar after a successful refresh.
*
* @param {Object} widget The refresh area widget.
*/
,postRefreshHandler: function(widget) {
var controller = this;
var renderContext = this.renderContext;
cursor_clear();
var refreshUrl = controller.url;
var emsName = "";
var indexOfEMSName = refreshUrl.indexOf("emsName=", 0);
if(indexOfEMSName >= 0){
emsName = refreshUrl.substring(indexOfEMSName+8);
if (emsName.indexOf("&") >= 0) {
emsName = emsName.substring(0, emsName.indexOf("&"));
emsName = "script_" + emsName;
}
}
if (emsName != "") {
if (dojo.byId(emsName) != null) {
var espot = dojo.query('.genericESpot',dojo.byId(emsName).parentNode)[0];
if (espot != null) {
dojo.addClass(espot,'emptyESpot');
}
}
}
dojo.publish("CMPageRefreshEvent");
}
});
</script>

* Clears the progress bar after a successful refresh.

,postRefreshHandler: function(widget) {
var controller = this;
var renderContext = this.renderContext;
cursor_clear();
var refreshUrl = controller.url;
var emsName = "";
var indexOfEMSName = refreshUrl.indexOf("emsName=", 0);
if(indexOfEMSName >= 0){
emsName = refreshUrl.substring(indexOfEMSName+8);
if (emsName.indexOf("&") >= 0) {
emsName = emsName.substring(0, emsName.indexOf("&"));
emsName = "script_" + emsName;
}
}
if (emsName != "") {
if (dojo.byId(emsName) != null) {
var espot = dojo.query('.genericESpot',dojo.byId(emsName).parentNode)[0];
if (espot != null) {
dojo.addClass(espot,'emptyESpot');
}
}
}
dojo.publish("CMPageRefreshEvent");
}
});
</script>

$( "#globalFooterEspot" ).hide();
}

hideFooter();
}else{
$( "#globalFooterEspot" ).show();
}

GoogleMapJS.mapOptions = {
scaleControl: true,
overviewMapControl: true,
overviewMapControlOptions:{opened:true},
mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP
};
GoogleMapJS.map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById('googleMap'), GoogleMapJS.mapOptions);
GoogleMapJS.geocoder = new google.maps.Geocoder();
GoogleMapJS.map.setCenter(new google.maps.LatLng(GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[0].latitude,GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[0].longitude), 5);
},
reset:function() {
GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo = [];
for (var i=0; i<GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location.length; i++) {
GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].visited = 0;
}
},
geocodeAddress:function(passFunction) {
var address = document.getElementById('findDesignHelpInput').value;
GoogleMapJS.geocoder.geocode({'address' : address + ' USA'}, function(results, status) {
if (status === 'OK') {
GoogleMapJS.visitorAddressInfo.latitude = results[0].geometry.location.lat();
GoogleMapJS.visitorAddressInfo.longitude = results[0].geometry.location.lng();
GoogleMapJS.visitorAddressInfo.address = address;
GoogleMapJS.map.setCenter(results[0].geometry.location);
passFunction();
}
});
},
loadVisitorsStores:function() {
var visitorLatLng = new google.maps.LatLng(GoogleMapJS.visitorAddressInfo.latitude,GoogleMapJS.visitorAddressInfo.longitude);
var storeLatLng;
var distance;
// calculate and populate distance to each store from user's address
for (var i=0; i<GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location.length; i++) {
storeLatLng = new google.maps.LatLng(GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].latitude,GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].longitude);
distance = Math.round(google.maps.geometry.spherical.computeDistanceBetween(storeLatLng,visitorLatLng, 3963.19)*100)/100;
GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].distance = distance;
}
// store 5-closest stores in visitorStoreInfo[] array
var shortestDistance, shortestDistanceIndex;
for (var j=0; (j<GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location.length) && j<4; j++) {
shortestDistance = 10000000;
shortestDistanceIndex = i;
for (var i=0; i<GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location.length; i++) {
if(GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].visited != 1 && GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].excluded!=true) {
if (GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].distance < shortestDistance) {
shortestDistance = GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[i].distance;
shortestDistanceIndex = i;
}
}
}
GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[j] = shortestDistanceIndex;
GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[shortestDistanceIndex].visited = 1;
}
},
displayVisitorsStores:function() {
$("#dhStoreList").empty();
var within100count = 0;
for (var i=0; i<4; i++) {
if(GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].distance <= 100) {
within100count++;
$('#dhStoreList').
append('<li>' +
'<label for="storeResult_'+ GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].storeId + '"' + i + '>'
+ '<input type="radio" name="storeResult" id="storeResult_'+ GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].storeId + '" value="' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].storeId + '" />'
+ '<div class="storeInfo">'
+ '<div class="storeName">' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].name + '</div>'
+ '<div class="storeAddress">' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].address1
+ ', ' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].city
+ ', ' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].state
+ ' ' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].zip
+ '</div>'
+ '<div class="storePhone">' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].phone + '</div>'
+ '<div class="approxDist italic"> approx ' + GoogleMapJS.hvtStoresInfo.location[GoogleMapJS.visitorStoreInfo[i]].distance + ' miles</div>'
+ '</div>'
+'</label>'
+'</li>');
}
}
if(within100count == 0) {
$('#storeListMessage').html("We're sorry but Havertys does not serve your area.");
} else if(within100count == 1) {
$('#storeListMessage').html("We've found a showroom near you!");
} else if(within100count > 1) {
$('#storeListMessage').html("We found several locations to serve you. Which would you prefer?");
}
$('.designHelpQuestion, .fewDetails, #popupFooter .submitLocation').hide();
$('#requestDesignHelp .storeList, #popupFooter .backStep, #popupFooter').show();
if(within100count >= 1) {
$('.contactMe').show();
}
}
}
